data.description: GORGEOUS!! What a stunning place to call home! Located in the highly-desired Preston Manor neighborhood & Frenship ISD, this beautiful 3/2/2 also features a sun-filled office just off the entry. The charming porch is straight out of a storybook. You'll appreciate the impressive details: vaulted ceiling, designer lighting, quartz counter tops, lots of natural light, and a new roof. The kitchen is captivating with floating shelves, subway tile, striking island and gas cooking. The isolated master suite is a true retreat with double vanities, relaxing soaker tub & spacious separate shower. The fantastic master closet also connects to the laundry room. Both the front & back porches feature attractive wood ceilings. Fabulously located in a quiet cul-de-sac just steps from a delightful park with pond, walking trails & disc golf. Located close to the lovely Preston Manor Dog Park. Other neighborhood amenities include 3 pools, tennis courts & fitness facility. Simply a remarkable home
